    "name": "Relative Hemolysis Index acceptance criterion",
    "description": "The CFD model shall predict a relative hemolysis index RH < 1.0 for all five evaluated flow-speed operating conditions, demonstrating that the subject device does not exceed predicate device hemolysis levels. This requirement is derived from FDA guidance on pump hemolysis evaluation.",
    "source": "https://doi.org/10.1115/1.4035918"
